{"tid":1154512,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"小學生分享國產零食 10人疑集體食物中毒送院","createTime":"2019-05-14T10:44:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-14T10:48:06.000Z","uid":122,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"72ea36a129522c466593ca5c3b782211049329a0","tid":1154512,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T10:44:51.000Z","msg":"中午12時半，秀茂坪觀塘官立小學（秀明道）懷疑有學生吃了不潔食物後不適，部份人嘔吐。多部救護車到場，由救護員替學童檢查後，10名學童送院。其間部份學童的家長趕到，陪同子女送院。<br />\n<br />\n消息指，5男5女小學生，<span style=\"color: red;\">分享其中一人在內地旅遊時所買的一包脆口零食</span>，其後有人嘔吐不適。<br />\n<br />\n觀塘官立小學（秀明道）陳副校長接受《蘋果》查詢時表示，涉及的10名同學為六年級同班同學，今早10時左右小息期間，他們分享自己帶回來的零食，其後當中3人嘔吐。其餘7人雖然未有異樣，但學校為安全起見，亦安排他們一併送院檢驗。<br />\n<br />\n陳副校表示，當時並不是午飯時間，未有進食飯盒，至於同學們分享的食物不只一種，目前仍了解食物的種類。"},{"pid":"89a0960b6d4e60846fdb707daee4aa23757dfa02","tid":1154512,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T10:45:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190514/59599097\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190514%2F59599097&d=%2Bo3sOR8bLgAbrAMBqI8fZ8FcVrLE0QCYyCuC44%2F36M0%3D&h=3838ae6c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190514%2F59599097&h=bbb47831\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190514/59599097</a>"},{"pid":"424ef3fb40650a5a2b5d5be941a3f1fcfd7060a7","tid":1154512,"uid":77092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T10:46:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"853d0ffd15a23406c8e730cf40cc4fd045ea921f","tid":1154512,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T10:48:04.000Z","msg":"拎去為狗都俾人告虐畜啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"695709169011d96185d7de7758e7ddac4b208908","tid":1154512,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"reply